trans-unit.source: Specifies the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView"></xref> entity that owns the cell style that was changed.
trans-unit.target: 지정 된 <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView"> </xref> 변경 된 셀 스타일을 소유 하 고 있는 엔터티.

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used by <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellStyleContentChangedEventArgs> to indicate which part of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> owns the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellStyle> that changed.
trans-unit.target: 이 열거형을 사용 하 여 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellStyleContentChangedEventArgs>의 어느 부분을 나타내는 데는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView>소유 하는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellStyle>변경.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellStyle> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellStyleContentChangedEventArgs>
